Follow OpenAI's product design aesthetic for all UI components and styling decisions.

## Design Principles
- Minimal, calm, and clean aesthetic
- Generous spacing throughout (use p-8, p-10, gap-8, mb-12+)
- Soft rounded corners (rounded-soft: 8px, rounded-softer: 12px)
- Subtle depth without heavy shadows (use borders instead of shadow-lg)
- Clear hierarchy with larger, confident headings (text-5xl/6xl)
- Neutral, modern typography (system fonts: -apple-system, Inter, Segoe UI)
- Smooth transitions (transition-smooth: 200ms, transition-smoother: 300ms)
- No visual clutter or decoration - focus on clarity

## Color System

### Light Mode
- Background: #FAFAFA (soft neutral gray, not pure white)
- Surface/Elevated: #FFFFFF (slightly darker than background)
- Primary Accent: #10A37F (OpenAI green)
- Text Primary: #1A1A1A (near black for readability)
- Text Secondary: #6B6B6B
- Border: #E5E5E5 (very subtle gray)

### Dark Mode
- Background: #1A1A1A (deep charcoal, not pure black)
- Surface/Elevated: #2A2A2A (slightly lighter for layering)
- Primary Accent: #19C37D (slightly brighter green)
- Text Primary: #E5E5E5 (soft white, never pure white)
- Text Secondary: #B0B0B0
- Border: #3A3A3A (subtle dark gray)

### CSS Variables
Use CSS custom properties defined in globals.css:
- var(--background)
- var(--surface)
- var(--accent)
- var(--text-primary)
- var(--text-secondary)
- var(--border)

## Component Patterns

### Selection States (Checkboxes, Toggle Buttons, Quick Actions)
**Active/Selected:**
- Border: 1px solid var(--accent)
- Background: rgba(16, 163, 127, 0.15) for light mode, rgba(25, 195, 125, 0.15) for dark mode (15% opacity green)
- Text: #FFFFFF (white)

**Inactive/Unselected:**
- Border: 1px solid var(--border)
- Background: transparent
- Text: var(--text-primary)

### Form Inputs
- Clean borders: 1px solid var(--border)
- Subtle focus states: border color changes to var(--accent), no heavy rings
- Padding: px-4 py-3
- Background: var(--background)
- Text: var(--text-primary)
- Border radius: rounded-soft (8px)

### Buttons
- Primary: Background var(--accent), white text, rounded-soft
- Hover: opacity-90, subtle scale or translate effects
- Active: opacity-95
- No heavy shadows - use subtle borders if needed

### Cards/Containers
- Background: var(--surface)
- Border: 1px solid var(--border)
- Padding: p-8 or p-10 (generous)
- Border radius: rounded-softer (12px)
- No shadows or very subtle (shadow-sm at most)

### Typography
- Headings: Larger, confident (h1: text-5xl/6xl, h2: text-3xl/4xl)
- Line height: 1.3 for headings, 1.6 for body
- Font weight: 600 for headings, 400-500 for body
- Letter spacing: -0.01em for headings

### Code Blocks
- Background: #FAFAFA (light) or #1E1E1E (dark)
- Border: 1px solid var(--border)
- Padding: 1.25rem
- Font: monospace, 0.875rem

## Spacing Guidelines
- Use generous spacing: space-y-8, gap-8, mb-12, mb-16
- Container padding: px-6 md:px-8, py-16 md:py-20
- Section spacing: mb-16 md:mb-20
- Form field spacing: space-y-8

## Transitions
- All interactive elements: transition-smooth (200ms ease)
- Hover states: opacity changes, subtle transforms
- Focus states: border color changes, no heavy rings
- Theme switching: smooth color transitions

## Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Generous spacing scales appropriately
- Touch targets appropriately sized
- Maintain readability at all breakpoints

## Tone
- Friendly, calm, and helpful
- No clutter, no visual noise
- Focus on clarity, not decoration
- Should feel like it could live inside an OpenAI product